BFB7AEC1.title: 'Beaver Gets Spelled'
BFB7AEC1.path: ../Leave it to Beaver/Leave it to Beaver - 001 Beaver Gets Spelled.mp4
BFB7AEC1.description: Beaver expects the worst when teacher Miss Canfield sends him home with a sealed note for his parents.

6F71955A.title: The Haircut
6F71955A.path: ../Leave it to Beaver/Leave it to Beaver - 004 The Haircut.mp4
6F71955A.description: Beaver loses the money he was given for a haircut. In order to conceal his carelessness from his parents, he gives himself a haircut.

5A8CA9E9.title: New Neighbors
5A8CA9E9.path: ../Leave it to Beaver/Leave it to Beaver - 005 New Neighbors.mp4
5A8CA9E9.description: June sends Beaver with a welcome-to-the-neighborhood bouquet to new next-door neighbor Mrs. Donaldson; but when the little boy is rewarded with a kiss on his cheek, rascally Eddie Haskell warns that a jealous Mr. Donaldson will soon show up at Beaver's door.

CE0C305F.title: Captain Jack
CE0C305F.path: ../Leave it to Beaver/Leave it to Beaver - 002 Captain Jack.mp4
CE0C305F.description: Wally and Beaver secretly order a Florida alligator from a comic book ad, planning to keep the creature in their bathtub.

D969F010.title: The Black Eye
D969F010.path: ../Leave it to Beaver/Leave it to Beaver - 003 The Black Eye.mp4
D969F010.description: Violet Rutherford gives Beaver a black eye.
